Field maps
: RGB channels for Φ, 𝒗, S
Entropy flowlines
: visualize "semantic winds"
Attractor detection
: convergence points = mnemonic compression
Symbol stability index (φ_RSVP)
: quantifies whether the sigil created a stable "meaning basin"
